SERVO 1:
    pin 3 -> servo controller
    pin 2 -> right direction input
    pin 4 -> left direction input
SERVO 2:
    pin 9 -> servo controller
    pin 7 -> right direction input
    pin 8 -> left direction input

MOTOR 1:
    pin A0 -> speed input
    pin 5 -> speed controller
    pin A2 -> direction input
    pin 11 -> direction controller
MOTOR 2:
    pin A1 -> speed input
    pin 6 -> speed controller
    pin A3 -> direction input
    pin 12 -> direction controller